svg.title: Opera market share in Eastern and Central Europe
svg.desc: Every country has an id which is its ISO-3116-1-ALPHA2 code in lower case. Members of the EU have a class="eu", countries in europe (which I found turkey to be but russia not) have a class="europe". Image based on a map (http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Image:Europe_countries.svg) by Julio "Tintazul" Reis. made by Marian "maix" Sigler. Released under CreativeCommons Attribution ShareAlike (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.5/). Updated by David Storey to include Opera market share taken from April 2009 figures from StatCounter, and related infographics and text labels.
